punar aniyamena darśayann āha. svayam ātmanā parāyatto vā sattvārthakriyāyāṃ pravṛttaḥ.

<commentary>kiṃ punar evam aniyamenābhidhīyata ity āha.

yasmāt sarvākāraṃ sarvavastutattvam adhigamya sarveṣāṃ hitasukhavidhānārtham udyacchadbhir buddhasutaiḥ na tad asti kiṃcit yan na śikṣitavyam. anyathā sarvākāraḥ sarvasattvānām arthaḥ kartum aśakyaḥ. puṇyasaṃbhāro 'pi evaṃ vicarato 'paryanta eva syāt.</commentary>

iyam api śikṣāpadamudrāvadhārayitavyety āha.